{"tid":699284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有懶人包]一地兩檢關注組學界組: JUN14,7pm立會集會","createTime":"2018-06-12T11:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T10:45:20.000Z","uid":47359,"like":12,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d8f51728703b85a9df792a3ae565b649fde5f9","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/194037_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F194037_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2ec807c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/194043_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F194043_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e93adbc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a773ab2c1075a6eac9e860312597c7590dd3811","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:44:44.000Z","msg":"甚麼是一地兩檢?<br />\n<br />\n在香港境內設立內地口岸區<br />\n執行中國法。美其名方便通關, 實則引公安進城, 意圖逐步破壞一國兩制"},{"pid":"f053b4cb999a199368a381987d37b4c59f3d20c2","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:47:47.000Z","msg":"一地兩檢違憲?<br />\n<br />\n基本法18條<br />\n<br />\n內容: 只有有關國防, 外交和不屬於香港自治範圍的全國性法律才能列入基本法附件三並於香港實施<br />\n<br />\n問題: 基本法第18條列明全國性法律不會在港實施的保障將會失效"},{"pid":"d82f07ed6b0cd87b08dce5038522cb6efa674fa5","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:51:15.000Z","msg":"基本法第19條<br />\n<br />\n內容: 香港享有獨立司法權及對特區內所有案件的審判權<br />\n<br />\n問題: 香港法院對內地口岸區內所有事宜的管轄權均被刪除, 而內地法院將擁有這些事宜的管轄權"},{"pid":"efc9aefbfa5236732d5241beacbc3ea4475468ea","tid":699284,"uid":73915,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:52:42.000Z","msg":"立法會就立法會，立乜撚野會？"},{"pid":"bbb0c179a29eb7e8420ddbdf2a49d24d21bed0f7","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:59:20.000Z","msg":"基本法第22條<br />\n<br />\n內容: 中央政府不得干預香港自行管理的事務; 中央政府設立的一切機構及所屬人員於香港境內均須遵守特區的法律<br />\n<br />\n問題: 中國人員公然在香港境內執法, 破壞香港運作體系"},{"pid":"1ee2a76c87eee18cdb1ad20bf13851ca64b8802e","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efc9aefbfa5236732d5241beacbc3ea4475468ea","tid":699284,"uid":73915,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:52:42.000Z","msg":"立法會就立法會，立乜撚野會？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"ok改正<br />\n 立法會立法會立法會"},{"pid":"d46b6f19d079304e1249783c00a87485463bc8e8","tid":699284,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6280bc6b11a85946d27f97ae13e792616f4054b5","tid":699284,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:05:36.000Z","msg":"都就黎立法通過法案啦，仲係到討乜撚野論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad424fd04cc91f24cc71fa05ab119fe2a2af4fd2","tid":699284,"uid":116530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/200632_542910cc57354a6e347743fb97746413.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F200632_542910cc57354a6e347743fb97746413.png&h=b29c3a48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92155216c668e7e5ef0cf2554efe017f76b01792","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:07:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1e873ce32765fd9398ff5db2caf2e30875ea19a","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"一地兩檢唔止係法律問題<br />\n<br />\n西九割地只係開始, 今日割一忽, 聽日又一忽。邊界隨住列車移動, 香港嘅司法管轄範圍被蠶食, 香港人失去的不止是一個口岸區, 而是一直引以為傲的自由及核心價值"},{"pid":"847b319749a7cb3e0d925f09e4633faa26e4e501","tid":699284,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c10f62a58dc386de472709e8f7b05538fa22b11","tid":699284,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4830ed54238d664a92c758127f7a1ef798639419","tid":699284,"uid":133680,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c10f62a58dc386de472709e8f7b05538fa22b11","tid":699284,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:15:02.000Z","msg":"學獨聯又改組？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a08c889f27ec9caf76a1159c31f00dfaaf7b380","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92155216c668e7e5ef0cf2554efe017f76b01792","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:07:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:33:58.000Z","msg":"二五蔣又出賣前組織成員資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/203250_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F203250_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=cf04209d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"770767636aaa7f20ad0991631a6c0e6565002afa","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:34:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e55fe0385511241b2cbf4c15a7d54642e45b49e6","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ad424fd04cc91f24cc71fa05ab119fe2a2af4fd2","tid":699284,"uid":116530,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,