 />\n<br />\n&ldquo;犯罪思想不會導致死亡，犯罪思想本身就是死亡。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n故事主角史密斯亦稱犯罪思想是唯一可怕的罪惡。"},{"pid":"793fbc07292afe208521a4a1a9cb03eb1b2a5e6d","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T23:26:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85af224d13518e7daa2638569f92c96638e74478","tid":699284,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"793fbc07292afe208521a4a1a9cb03eb1b2a5e6d","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c2ce5aed390e5a89bf2a5892df98394a0a3105d","tid":699284,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d23bdf8075957413b1296925c0882158d9126baf","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:25:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T22:08:41.000Z","msg":"我都無搵鄧家彪，思想犯罪？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T23:26:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:39:21.000Z","msg":"1.無做到<br />\n2.「屈」你係HK01，但你唔敢出聲，淨係識遷怒於我"},{"pid":"2ffd352a5ba7abfa283c23cf1f895e89850780ba","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:40:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bddea727f9803c94af034edb23f79fcade7efabf","tid":699284,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ffd352a5ba7abfa283c23cf1f895e89850780ba","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"85af224d13518e7daa2638569f92c96638e74478","tid":699284,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"793fbc07292afe208521a4a1a9cb03eb1b2a5e6d","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T23:26:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:39:21.000Z","msg":"1.無做到<br />\n2.「屈」你係HK01，但你唔敢出聲，淨係識遷怒於我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:40:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T01:43:12.000Z","msg":"唔夠人講又發爛渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj