"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1dff381d6152341341302834c986e211f6add05","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:37:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:59:55.000Z","msg":"會員蔣介石(翻生)被踢後將組織前成員個人資料公開<br />\n毫無政治道德<br />\n更聯同五毛攻擊學獨聯<br />\n<br />\n100個讚，有關sir型仔照<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/678081/25?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/678081/25?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/140548_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F140548_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=6d175de3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/140310_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F140310_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=413a6c21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1bd962de4304977924453c8214a0abe5b9257b3","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:02:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c58429c6f82b4c20af8dcc57c17adf8b4a9b6646","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bddb103fc08c9fe848760da005e71ea552e4fe4","tid":699284,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8336b0155d5d194e11834531a95ae8675adefc18","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bddb103fc08c9fe848760da005e71ea552e4fe4","tid":699284,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:06:35.000Z","msg":"一地兩檢關注組和平集會<br />\n你隻五毛咪撚戇鳩"},{"pid":"2b6c0eed2845ce2a46da14bac9454ececb181a70","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"[回帶] 涂謹申: 港可割讓西九站土地 避免一地兩檢牴觸基本法<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/692439/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/692439/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"5b40204394771ef84495ee86d7279ce1429b4c03","tid":699284,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:11:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持關sir! </span>"},{"pid":"5ab76250ab0f3764bac74c574cc42ba8e25a5f65","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:13:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fe948f82a9b64ea3385db8cf808570dc11d33b6","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:14:37.000Z","msg":"【旺角騷亂】主審法官彭寶琴個人資料<br />\n2018-05-1817.9K<br />\n即時要聞<br />\n <br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n姓名：彭寶琴（洋名Anthea）<br />\n<br />\n年齡：56歲<br />\n<br />\n資歷：<br />\n1985年在香港大學取得社會科學學士學位，1993年通過英國曼徹斯特城市大學的法律專業共同試，翌年在港獲認許為大律師。<br />\n1995年加入律政署出任檢察官， 在民事法律科下的民事訴訟組工作；3年後晉升為高級政府律師，被調派至刑事檢控科，其後在基本法、人權、 投訴警察、淫褻物品及賭博組工作，並於2001年考取香港大學法學碩士學位。<br />\n2007年晉升為副首席政府律師，2010年獲委任為區域法院法官，2013年11月15日獲委任為高等法院原訟法庭法官至今。<br />\n<br />\n婚姻狀況：<br />\n亡夫歐陽國基生前為水警總區總部（行政）警司，2016年底疑因隱性心臟病突發在鯉景灣住所猝死，彭當時身在外地，由歐陽的水警同袍登門揭發事故。<br />\n<br />\n曾審理案件：<br />\n東方明珠石油前副主席劉夢熊涉串謀詐騙案；開埠首宗無屍體無法證無招認的謀殺案重審、最終被告陳文琛仍謀殺罪成等。"},{"pid":"828fabddbe6c8d87c1bca6c3cea5ae74ebf6d37c","tid":699284,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1bd962de4304977924453c8214a0abe5b9257b3","tid":699284,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeb47478e6cc1d156bca60fce296448753472047","tid":699284,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1dff381d6152341341302834c986e211f6add05",